policy_name: Admins can view all login logs
using_expression:
(EXISTS ( SELECT 1
   FROM auth.users
  WHERE ((users.id = auth.uid()) AND ((users.role)::text = 'admin'::text))))

policy_name: Users can view their own login logs
Enable realtime for users own ticket messages
using_expression:
(EXISTS ( SELECT 1
   FROM support_tickets
  WHERE ((support_tickets.id = support_ticket_messages.ticket_id) AND ((support_tickets.user_id = auth.uid()) OR (EXISTS ( SELECT 1
           FROM vb_cdz_gus_user_profile_tb
          WHERE ((vb_cdz_gus_user_profile_tb.id = auth.uid()) AND (vb_cdz_gus_user_profile_tb."isAdmin" = true))))))))

policy_name: Users can create messages on accessible tickets
with_check_expression:
(ticket_id IN ( SELECT support_tickets.id
   FROM support_tickets
  WHERE (auth.uid() IN ( SELECT vb_cdz_gus_user_profile_tb.id
           FROM vb_cdz_gus_user_profile_tb
          WHERE (vb_cdz_gus_user_profile_tb.id = support_tickets.user_id)
        UNION
         SELECT up.id
           FROM (vb_cdz_gus_user_profile_tb up
             JOIN vb_cdz_gus_companies_tb c ON ((c.id = up.company)))
          WHERE (c.id = support_tickets.company_id)))))
